<item>
            <title>[LU-7414] out_read() uses both tti_u.update and tti_u.rdbuf members of the same union</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7414</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;out_read()&lt;/tt&gt; uses fields from both the &lt;tt&gt;update&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;rdbuf&lt;/tt&gt; members of the &lt;tt&gt;tti_u&lt;/tt&gt; union in &lt;tt&gt;struct tgt_thread_info&lt;/tt&gt;.  This can lead to data corruption since those fields of the union are overlapping in memory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="33080">LU-7414</key>
